        AI project manager focused on turning ambiguous AI opportunities into
        reusable systems, practical workflows, and documented delivery knowledge.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>Focus</h2>
      <p>
        This site is the home base for technical writing, project records, and
        long-term thinking around AI engineering and knowledge management.
      </p>
      <h2>Operating principle</h2>
      <p>
        Start from the problem, keep the architecture simple, and make every
        workflow reproducible.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

